Estimate Landscape Parameters

Source: R/estimate_parameters.R
estimate_parameters.Rd

Used to get parameters for virtual landscape creation functions create_landscape and add_lines

Usage

estimate_parameters(landscape, curve = NA, line = NA)

Arguments

landscape

matrix with integer values representing different land-cover classes

curve

list each element of the list contains a) class label and b) overlapping (polygon) classes

line

list each element of the list contains a) class label and b) connected (polygon) classes

Value

estimation of parameters of the given landscape

Examples

estimate_parameters(landscape, 5, 4)
